WEBVTT

00:11.100 --> 00:11.999
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "GREENLEAF"...</i>

00:12.001 --> 00:13.065
THIS HAS TO BE KEPT
IN THE FAMILY.

00:13.067 --> 00:14.265
WHO ELSE WOULD I TELL?

00:14.267 --> 00:15.699
SEND BOB
THE RECORDING.

00:15.701 --> 00:17.599
WRITE THE E-MAIL, WHATEVER.
JUST DO IT.

00:17.601 --> 00:21.132
YOU LIED TO KEEP YOUR SON
OUT OF JAIL.

00:21.134 --> 00:23.665
IF YOU STEP DOWN, I WON'T SHARE
THIS PROOF WITH THE POLICE.

00:23.667 --> 00:25.065
IT IS SO RARE
TO FIND A MAN

00:25.067 --> 00:27.398
WHO CAN SATISFY ONE WOMAN,
LET ALONE TWO.

00:27.400 --> 00:29.798
HE DOES HAVE A GIFT
IN PLEASING OTHERS.

00:29.800 --> 00:31.265
DON'T I KNOW IT.

00:31.267 --> 00:33.532
WHAT WERE YOU DOING AT FERNANDO
AMABLE'S OFFICE THE OTHER DAY?

00:33.534 --> 00:34.965
Woman:
WHERE WERE YOU

00:34.967 --> 00:38.599
THE DOZENS OF NIGHTS
THAT I SPENT ALONE IN OUR BED?

00:38.601 --> 00:40.365
YOU'RE DANTE SAUNDERS?

00:40.367 --> 00:41.498
YOU WANT
TO GO FOR A RIDE?

00:41.500 --> 00:43.565
I CAN DO WHATEVER I WANT
WITH WHOEVER I WANT.

00:43.567 --> 00:45.098
I'M SO HAPPY
YOU'RE GOING BACK TO SCHOOL.

00:45.100 --> 00:46.331
I'M NOT.

00:46.333 --> 00:47.899
THE MOST SENIOR GREENLEAF
EMPLOYED AT CALVARY

00:47.901 --> 00:50.465
CAN ALWAYS CAST THE TIE-BREAKING
VOTE IN BOARD DISPUTES.

00:50.467 --> 00:51.599
KEEP HER HAPPY.

00:51.601 --> 00:53.531
WE'RE GOING TO BE
NEEDING HER VOTE.

00:53.533 --> 00:54.998
I HAVE SOME NEWS
ABOUT THE HOUSE

00:55.000 --> 00:56.532
YOU MIGHT FIND
VERY INTERESTING,

00:56.534 --> 00:59.132
THE ONE THAT YOU COULD VERY WELL
BE THE OWNER OF ONE DAY.

00:59.134 --> 01:02.532
JUST GOING TO LEFT YOU,
GRACE, AND CHARITY.

01:02.534 --> 01:03.999
MAYBE THEY COULD
BUY US OUT.

01:04.001 --> 01:05.998
YOU GET UP THERE
ON SUNDAY,

01:06.000 --> 01:07.898
YOU SPEAK
YOUR OWN TRUTH,

01:07.900 --> 01:09.032
AND YOU WILL.

01:09.034 --> 01:10.832
DON'T DO IT, CHILD.
PLEASE DON'T DO IT.

01:10.834 --> 01:14.998
I'M STEPPING DOWN AS THE HEAD
PASTOR OF CALVARY FELLOWSHIP.

01:15.000 --> 01:17.931
[ CONGREGATION MURMURING ]

01:17.933 --> 01:25.799
♪♪

01:47.701 --> 01:50.498
I'M SO SORRY.
PLEASE DON'T DO THIS.

01:50.500 --> 01:52.498
I'M SO SORRY.

01:52.500 --> 01:58.965
♪♪

01:58.967 --> 02:00.732
[ MURMURING CONTINUES ]

02:00.734 --> 02:10.398
♪♪

02:10.400 --> 02:12.332
WORRIED SICK ABOUT YOU.

02:12.334 --> 02:14.332
♪♪

02:14.334 --> 02:17.465
WHAT FINALLY
BROUGHT YOU BACK, HUH?

02:17.467 --> 02:18.899
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

02:18.901 --> 02:20.765
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
YOU'VE BEEN CALLING ME NONSTOP.

02:20.767 --> 02:22.565
SOPHIA CALLED,
LAID ALL THAT ON ME.

02:22.567 --> 02:23.965
MY MOM
IS GOING TO GO TO JAIL.

02:23.967 --> 02:26.065
NO, I MEAN
WHAT ARE YOU DOING<i> HERE?</i>

02:26.067 --> 02:28.598
I'M GOING TO TURN
MYSELF IN.

02:28.600 --> 02:32.732
[ CHATTER ]

02:32.734 --> 02:35.665
♪♪

02:45.834 --> 02:47.632
♪ AMEN ♪

02:50.667 --> 02:51.732
♪ ALL RIGHT ♪

02:51.734 --> 02:53.132
♪ AMEN ♪

02:53.134 --> 02:56.065
♪ UH-HUH, HMM ♪

02:56.067 --> 02:58.565
♪ OOH-OOH, OOH ♪

03:01.800 --> 03:03.132
♪ WELL ♪

03:06.467 --> 03:09.598
♪ OH-OHH, OHH ♪

03:09.600 --> 03:14.932
♪ OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH ♪

03:14.934 --> 03:17.999
♪ AMEN, AMEN ♪
♪ OH ♪

03:21.400 --> 03:23.198
♪ YEAH ♪

03:23.200 --> 03:26.198
