 www.vitac.com

03:26.200 --> 03:29.199
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

03:32.934 --> 03:42.998
♪♪

03:43.000 --> 03:47.198
♪♪

03:47.200 --> 03:49.365
Man: WHAT THE HELL
HAPPENED HERE?

03:49.367 --> 03:52.098
GRACE WAS
A KEY PART OF MY PLAN.

03:52.100 --> 03:54.232
DID I NOT MAKE THAT CLEAR
TO THE TWO OF YOU?

03:54.234 --> 03:55.865
IT WAS
OUT OF OUR HANDS.

03:55.867 --> 03:57.665
IN GRACE'S DEFENSE,
I DON'T THINK IN ANY WAY

03:57.667 --> 03:59.065
SHE EXPECTED
THIS SON OF HERS

03:59.067 --> 04:00.699
TO SHOW UP
WHEN SHE TOOK THIS JOB.

04:00.701 --> 04:03.165
AND THE SECRET SON --
HE'S HERE?

04:03.167 --> 04:04.899
I BELIEVE HE IS,
YES.

04:04.901 --> 04:06.398
WHAT,
IT'S A MATTER OF BELIEF?

04:06.400 --> 04:09.499
HE'S FALLEN IN LOVE
WITH A SINGER.

04:09.501 --> 04:10.699
SHE CALLED,

04:10.701 --> 04:14.199
TOLD HIM THE KID'S
STAYING AT THE MANSION.

04:14.201 --> 04:18.098
AND GRACE
HAS STEPPED DOWN.

04:18.100 --> 04:18.965
WHY?

04:18.967 --> 04:20.565
APPARENTLY,
SHE LIED TO THE POLICE

04:20.567 --> 04:23.031
TO PROVIDE HIM WITH AN ALIBI
AFTER HE ROBBED A PHARMACY,

04:23.033 --> 04:24.032
AND SHE --
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:24.034 --> 04:25.531
THIS FAMILY.

04:25.533 --> 04:28.531
I THOUGHT
SHE WAS DIFFERENT.

04:28.533 --> 04:29.999
AND WHAT ABOUT
MY BOARD?

04:30.001 --> 04:32.231
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO
GET ME MY MAJORITY.

04:32.233 --> 04:34.565
THE GREENLEAFS
KNEW ABOUT THE BRIBE.

04:34.567 --> 04:36.598
I WANT THE BOARD
TO MEET TOMORROW,

04:36.600 --> 04:39.665
AND I WANT THE VOTE
TO GO OUR WAY.

04:39.667 --> 04:42.465
I'M SICK OF WAITING FOR PEOPLE
TO DO US FAVORS.

04:42.467 --> 04:43.598
I NEED CONTROL.

04:43.600 --> 04:45.132
I'LL MAKE SURE
YOU GET IT, DADDY.

04:45.134 --> 04:46.865
YOU WON'T BE
DOING ANYTHING.

04:46.867 --> 04:48.798
YOU'RE GOING BACK
TO PHOENIX TODAY.

04:48.800 --> 04:50.665
BUT IT WASN'T
MY FAULT!

04:50.667 --> 04:52.665
IF THE BEST
YOU CAN DO IS,

04:52.667 --> 04:55.465
"IT WASN'T MY FAULT,"
THEN IT IS!

05:07.000 --> 05:09.798
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

05:09.800 --> 05:11.932
DID YOU
HAVE SOMETHING TO DO

05:11.934 --> 05:15.598
WITH GRACE
STEPPING DOWN?

05:15.600 --> 05:17.732
BECAUSE SOMETHING TELLS ME
YOU DID.

05:17.734 --> 05:19.665
I DID IMPRESS UPON HER
THE DAMAGE SHE CAN DO

05:19.667 --> 05:23.065
TO THE DENOMINATION'S BRAND
IF IT CAME OUT THAT SHE LIED.

05:23.067 --> 05:24.265
UH-HUH.

05:24.267 --> 05:27.099
AND YOU, UH,
YOU'RE IN LOVE

05:27.101 --> 05:30.031
WITH THIS --
THIS SINGER?

05:30.033 --> 05:32.232
CHARITY.
BUT IT'S A GOOD THING.

05:32.234 --> 05:34.932
OH, I'M LOOKING FORWARD
TO HEARING ABOUT HOW.

05:34.934 --> 05:36.665
SHE'D BE VERY USEFUL

05:36.667 --> 05:40.065
IN WAYS THAT WOULD TAKE A MOMENT
TO EXPLAIN.

05:40.067 --> 05:42.798
I'M STILL NOT OVER
HOW YOU HURT JUDY.

05:42.800 --> 05:44.965
YOU KNOW THAT,
DON'T YOU?

05:44.967 --> 05:47.598
YES, SIR, I DO.

05:47.600 --> 05:49.965
SHE STILL HOLDS A TORCH
FOR YOU.

05:51.334 --> 05:53.732
I THINK
THAT'S HALF OF WHY

05:53.734 --> 05:56.332
THIS DIDN'T WORK OUT
WITH KEN.

05:56.334 --> 05:59.332
I DID WHAT I FELT WAS RIGHT
AT THE TIME

05:59.334 --> 06:00.765
FOR MYSELF AND JUDY.

06:02.967 --> 06:04.698
WHAT A MESS.

06:04.700 --> 06:14.698
♪♪

06:14.700 --> 06:18.132
♪♪

06:18.134 --> 06:21.598
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

06:21.600 --> 06:23.465
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

06:23.467 --> 06:33.098
♪♪

06:33.100 --> 06:38.865
♪♪

06:38.867 --> 06:42.065
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

06:42.067 --> 06:44.065
COME IN.

06:44.067 --> 06:48.065
♪♪

06:48.067 --> 06:52.065
[ SIGHS ]

06:52.067 --> 06:54.198
THIS HOUSE,
THIS LAND...

06:54.200 --> 06:56.332
IT'S ALL
WE HAVE LEFT NOW.

06:56.334 --> 06:59.865
♪♪

06:59.867 --> 07:01.865
I'M SO SCARED.

07:01.867 --> 07:04.265
♪♪

07:04.267 --> 07:07.798
[ SIGHS ]

07:07.800 --> 07:11.798
♪♪

07:11.800 --> 07:15.065
MAMA...

07:16.467 --> 07:18.065
...I JUST WANTED
TO LET YOU KNOW

07:18.067 --> 07:21.398
I HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH PHIL AND...

07:21.400 --> 07:24.632
WITH THE WAY
HE PRESSURED GIGI.

07:24.634 --> 07:27.432
SO, WHERE DID
THIS PROOF COME FROM

07:27.434 --> 07:29.265
HE TOLD HER HE HAD?

07:29.267 --> 07:31.265
HMM?

07:31.267 --> 07:33.398
WHERE?

07:33.400 --> 07:38.532
DOES PHIL HAVE
THIS WHOLE PLACE BUGGED?

07:38.534 --> 07:41.932
DOES HE HAVE CONFEDERATES
AND UNMARKED VANS

07:41.934 --> 07:46.965
OUT ON THE ROAD
WITH EARPIECES AND 7/11 COFFEE?

07:51.534 --> 07:54.199
I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE.

07:54.201 --> 07:56.065
SO, YOU CAME IN HERE
TO LIE TO ME?

07:57.833 --> 08:00.765
BUT YOU KNOW WHAT,
CHARITY?

08:00.767 --> 08:02.731
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:02.733 --> 08:04.032
BABY...

08:04.034 --> 08:09.065
I'M NOT MAD AT YOU
ABOUT ANY OF THIS.

08:09.067 --> 08:10.798
NONE OF IT.

08:10.800 --> 08:14.198
BECAUSE, YOU SEE,
I KNOW THAT YOU ARE NO MORE

08:14.200 --> 08:17.532
THAN PHIL'S
HELPLESS LITTLE PAWN.

08:17.534 --> 08:20.532
BUT IF YOU CAME IN HERE
TO LIE IN MY FACE

08:20.534 --> 08:23.265
WHEN YOU KNOW THAT
I HAVE JUST LOST EVERYTHING,

08:23.267 --> 08:26.099
I WILL BE.

08:26.101 --> 08:29.165
MAMA,
I NEVER MEANT TO HURT YOU.

08:29.167 --> 08:30.932
BUT YOU MEANT --

08:30.934 --> 08:33.932
YOU<i> MEANT --</i>
TO HURT YOUR SISTER.

08:35.301 --> 08:37.665
I JUST WANT MY LIFE.

08:37.667 --> 08:39.732
CHARITY...

08:39.734 --> 08:42.998
<i> YOUR</i> LIFE IS<i> MY</i> LIFE.

08:43.000 --> 08:46.598
MY LIFE IS GRACE'S.
GRACE'S IS A.J.'S,

08:46.600 --> 08:48.598
AND A.J.'S IS NATHAN'S.

08:48.600 --> 08:50.132
IT'S ONE LIFE.

08:50.134 --> 08:54.465
DO DAMAGE TO EVEN
ONE SMALL PART OF THAT LIFE,

08:54.467 --> 08:56.632
AND THE WHOLE LIFE
SUFFERS.

08:58.634 --> 09:00.332
AND THAT IS A LESSON

09:00.334 --> 09:03.732
THAT YOUR LITTLE GURU
PHIL DEMARS NEVER TAUGHT YOU

09:03.734 --> 09:08.732
BECAUSE HE DOESN'T
KNOW IT HIMSELF, BECAUSE...

09:08.734 --> 09:11.065
HE IS SMART ENOUGH

09:11.067 --> 09:14.665
TO MAKE A BIG FOOL
OUT OF YOU,

09:14.667 --> 09:17.099
AND THAT'S THE EXTENT
OF HIS GENIUS.

09:17.101 --> 09:26.565
♪♪

09:26.567 --> 09:30.199
[ FOOTSTEPS DEPART ]

09:30.201 --> 09:32.132
[ SIGHS ]

09:32.134 --> 09:33.465
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

09:33.467 --> 09:35.865
YOU CALL ME,
SOPHIA CALLED ME WHINING AT ME

09:35.867 --> 09:37.665
TO CALL YOU BACK,
TO COME BACK HOME.

09:37.667 --> 09:39.699
NOT TO
TURN YOURSELF IN.

09:39.701 --> 09:41.165
IF YOU GO AHEAD
WITH THIS PLAN --

09:41.167 --> 09:44.232
IT'S NOT "IF."
I'M DOING IT.

09:44.234 --> 09:46.032
YOU'LL PROBABLY
GET 10 YEARS.

09:46.034 --> 09:48.065
THEN THAT'S
WHAT I'LL GET.

09:51.300 --> 09:53.565
A.J.,
YOU STOLE THESE DRUGS.

09:53.567 --> 09:55.265
AARON THINKS
THAT WE CAN DEMONSTRATE

09:55.267 --> 09:56.965
THAT YOU'RE AN ADDICT.
I'M NOT AN ADDICT.

09:56.967 --> 09:59.732
I JUST WANT TO GO DOWN THERE
TOMORROW AND DO THIS.

10:01.267 --> 10:02.865
SO,
WHY NOT JUST GO NOW?

10:05.101 --> 10:07.332
I MEAN,
IF THAT'S YOUR PLAN.

10:09.367 --> 10:11.165
YOU WANT ME
TO GO RIGHT NOW?

10:11.167 --> 10:13.432
I DON'T WANT YOU
TO LEAVE AT ALL.

10:21.067 --> 10:22.932
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

10:23.901 --> 10:25.698
[ SIGHS ]

10:25.700 --> 10:27.365
I THINK HE'S SCARED
AND CONFUSED.

10:27.367 --> 10:28.232
YEAH.

10:28.234 --> 10:30.932
THERE'S SOMETHING
HE'S NOT SAYING.

10:30.934 --> 10:33.499
THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE.

10:33.501 --> 10:35.232
WHAT MAKES YOU
THINK THAT?

10:35.234 --> 10:36.598
NO ONE WANTS
TO GO TO PRISON.

10:36.600 --> 10:38.732
IF THEY HAD TRIED ME
FOR KILLING MAC,

10:38.734 --> 10:40.465
I WOULD'VE FOUGHT IT
THE WHOLE WAY.

10:40.467 --> 10:43.598
BUT THAT
WAS SELF-DEFENSE.

10:43.600 --> 10:45.765
SOMEHOW,
I THINK THIS IS, TOO.

10:47.600 --> 10:48.598
[ SIGHS ]

10:48.600 --> 10:50.465
WELL,
IT IS HIS DECISION.

10:50.467 --> 10:52.331
I MEAN,
AT SOME POINT,

10:52.333 --> 10:54.398
YOU MIGHT JUST HAVE TO
BE THANKFUL HE'S ALIVE

10:54.400 --> 10:55.898
AND MOVE ON.

10:55.900 --> 10:58.765
I'M NOT WILLING TO GIVE UP
JUST YET.

10:58.767 --> 11:00.998
WELL, WHO SAID ANYTHING
ABOUT GIVING UP?

11:01.000 --> 11:08.732
♪♪

11:11.834 --> 11:15.931
♪♪

11:15.933 --> 11:18.032
HEY, KERISSA.
YOU GOT A SECOND?

11:18.034 --> 11:20.265
A QUICK ONE.
WHY?

11:20.267 --> 11:23.132
I AM NOT GOING TO BE ABLE TO
BUY YOU AND JACOB OUT RIGHT NOW.

11:23.134 --> 11:25.465
I'M SO SORRY,
BUT A.J.'S SUDDENLY BACK.

11:25.467 --> 11:26.998
I GET IT.
THANKS ANYWAY.

11:27.000 --> 11:28.398
I'M SO SORRY.

11:28.400 --> 11:30.465
IT'S OKAY, ALL RIGHT?

11:30.467 --> 11:32.198
AND IT'S NOT YOU. I JUST
HAVE TO GET TO URGENT CARE.

11:32.200 --> 11:34.932
WHAT?
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

11:34.934 --> 11:36.765
OBVIOUSLY NOT.

11:37.734 --> 11:41.165
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

11:44.833 --> 11:46.832
YOU WANT
TO COME INSIDE?

11:46.834 --> 11:49.132
[ CHUCKLES ]
I CAN'T.

11:49.134 --> 11:50.265
WHY NOT?

11:50.267 --> 11:51.865
WHAT YOU GOT GOING ON
ON A SUNDAY, HUH?

11:51.867 --> 11:53.865
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO BE
THE BAD GIRL.

11:53.867 --> 11:56.265
[ LAUGHS ]

11:56.267 --> 11:57.932
YEAH,
I GUESS I AM.

11:57.934 --> 12:00.398
I WASN'T
GOING TO SAY ANYTHING,

12:00.400 --> 12:02.631
BUT MY BROTHER SHOWED UP
AT THE CHURCH TODAY.

12:02.633 --> 12:04.365
THE ONE WHO RAN OFF?

12:04.367 --> 12:06.898
YEAH,
HE'S BACK AT THE HOUSE,

12:06.900 --> 12:08.432
AND I KIND OF
NEED TO GO AND SEE HIM.

12:08.434 --> 12:09.498
ALL RIGHT.

12:09.500 --> 12:11.999
SO WHAT ABOUT
TOMORROW NIGHT?

12:12.001 --> 12:14.698
MAYBE.

12:14.700 --> 12:17.499
I'LL HIT YOU UP.
LET ME GET THAT.

12:26.067 --> 12:27.332
DRIVE SAFE, OKAY?

12:27.334 --> 12:29.598
OKAY.

12:29.600 --> 12:32.132
COME HERE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:32.134 --> 12:33.732
♪♪

12:33.734 --> 12:36.865
OH, PLEASE LET IT BE NEGATIVE.

12:36.867 --> 12:38.265
♪♪

12:38.267 --> 12:40.865
PLEASE, GOD, LET IT BE NEGATIVE.

12:40.867 --> 12:42.865
PLEASE. PLEASE.

12:42.867 --> 12:45.532
♪♪

12:45.534 --> 12:46.865
KERISSA...

12:46.867 --> 12:50.065
IT'S POSITIVE.
YOU HAVE CHLAMYDIA.

12:50.067 --> 12:52.198
I HAVE SOME
PREVENTATIVE MEASURES

12:52.200 --> 12:53.999
YOU CAN DISCUSS
WITH YOUR HUSBAND.

12:57.600 --> 13:00.598
I DIDN'T
CATCH IT FROM HIM.

13:00.600 --> 13:02.465
OH.

13:02.467 --> 13:04.165
THEN YOU MIGHT WANT
TO HAVE A CONVERSATION

13:04.167 --> 13:06.399
WITH WHOMEVER ELSE
YOU'VE BEEN SEEING SEXUALLY.

13:09.000 --> 13:11.398
TAKE ALL OF THEM
AND YOU'LL BE FINE,

13:11.400 --> 13:13.132
AND NO SEX
FOR 10 DAYS.

13:13.134 --> 13:15.065
OKAY.
THANK YOU.

13:15.067 --> 13:18.465
♪♪

13:18.467 --> 13:20.731
FIRST, IT WAS ALL THESE SEATS
ON THE BOARD,

13:20.733 --> 13:22.999
AND NOW THEY WANT US
TO VOTE TOMORROW

13:23.001 --> 13:25.065
ON THIS PROPOSAL.

13:25.067 --> 13:26.665
Man:
WHAT PROPOSAL?

13:26.667 --> 13:28.631
THEY WANT
TO DISSOLVE CALVARY

13:28.633 --> 13:30.232
AS A CORPORATION
ENTIRELY

13:30.234 --> 13:33.765
AND JUST MAKE IT
ONE BIG DIVISION OF H&H.

13:33.767 --> 13:35.765
WE WOULD
LOSE THE CHURCH FOREVER.

13:35.767 --> 13:37.132
HOLD ON A SECOND.

13:37.134 --> 13:38.465
NO,
HOW WOULD WE GET IT BACK?

13:38.467 --> 13:40.065
IT WON'T EVEN
TECHNICALLY EXIST.

13:40.067 --> 13:42.998
MAE, WE'VE BEEN TALKING
TO OUR ALLIES ON THE BOARD,

13:43.000 --> 13:46.198
AND WE THINK
NOW THAT CLARA'S COME ON,

13:46.200 --> 13:48.065
MAYBE WE CAN MAKE IT
A TIE VOTE.

13:48.067 --> 13:50.398
WHICH IS WHY WE THOUGHT
WE SHOULD COME TO YOU TWO

13:50.400 --> 13:51.598
AND TALK
TO YOU ABOUT --

13:51.600 --> 13:53.398
CHARITY.
THAT'S RIGHT.

13:53.400 --> 13:56.532
WHAT HAS THAT LITTLE IDIOT
DONE NOW?

13:59.334 --> 14:01.299
SHUT THE DOOR.

14:01.301 --> 14:02.565
WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU?

14:02.567 --> 14:04.699
ARE YOU
JUST USING ME?

14:04.701 --> 14:05.965
OH, THIS AGAIN?

14:05.967 --> 14:08.732
I COULD LOSE
MY FAMILY FOREVER.

14:10.033 --> 14:12.565
THEN WE'LL
START A NEW ONE.

14:12.567 --> 14:14.232
YEAH,
YOU SAY THAT.

14:14.234 --> 14:16.232
YOU SAY A LOT OF THINGS
LIKE THAT, BUT --

14:16.234 --> 14:19.265
CHARITY...

14:19.267 --> 14:22.665
BE STILL
AND KNOW THAT I AM --

14:22.667 --> 14:25.065
GOD?
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:25.067 --> 14:26.798
THE MAN
WHO LOVES YOU.

14:26.800 --> 14:32.132
♪♪

14:32.134 --> 14:34.398
WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO DO?

14:34.400 --> 14:37.198
THERE'S AN ARTICLE
IN THE BYLAWS THAT STATES

14:37.200 --> 14:39.532
IN THE EVENT OF A TIE
AMONG THE DEACONS,

14:39.534 --> 14:41.065
IT CAN BE BROKEN
BY A VOTE

14:41.067 --> 14:43.332
BY THE HIGHEST-RANKING MEMBER
OF THE GREENLEAF FAMILY

14:43.334 --> 14:45.265
STILL EMPLOYED
BY THE CHURCH.

14:45.267 --> 14:47.831
ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS CONVINCE CHARITY

14:47.833 --> 14:49.365
TO VOTE
WITH OUR FRIENDS HERE,

14:49.367 --> 14:52.231
AND THE CHURCH IS SAVED.
HMM?

14:52.233 --> 14:53.431
HMM.

14:53.433 --> 14:55.298
I'LL GO TALK TO CHARITY.

14:55.300 --> 14:58.565
♪♪

14:58.567 --> 15:01.232
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

15:01.234 --> 15:11.132
♪♪

15:11.134 --> 15:21.198
♪♪

15:21.200 --> 15:23.598
♪♪

15:23.600 --> 15:25.598
NOT TONIGHT.

15:25.600 --> 15:33.465
♪♪

15:33.467 --> 15:35.832
I SAID NOT TONIGHT,
JACOB.

15:37.734 --> 15:40.998
WHAT'D I DO NOW?

15:41.000 --> 15:42.999
NOTHING.
I JUST...

15:45.534 --> 15:47.832
I'M ON MY PERIOD,
AND I DON'T FEEL WELL.

15:51.200 --> 15:54.199
[ SIGHS ]
SORRY. I KNOW.

16:01.267 --> 16:03.332
FEEL BETTER,
OKAY?

16:03.334 --> 16:05.532
[ SIGHS ]

16:13.467 --> 16:15.699
SO NOW
YOU TWO WANT MY HELP?!

16:15.701 --> 16:17.599
WE DON'T<i> WANT</i> IT.
WE<i> NEED</i> IT.

16:19.267 --> 16:21.332
WHAT ABOUT WHAT I NEEDED
ALL THOSE YEARS, DADDY,

16:21.334 --> 16:23.798
WHEN IT WAS,
IT WAS GIGI, GIGI, GIGI?!

16:23.800 --> 16:25.065
CHARITY...

16:25.067 --> 16:28.465
I'M A PERSON.

16:28.467 --> 16:30.865
FINE.

16:30.867 --> 16:33.399
YOU'RE A PERSON.

16:36.067 --> 16:38.699
BUT IF
YOU KNOWINGLY DO THIS,

16:38.701 --> 16:41.632
TAKE EVERYTHING
YOUR MOTHER AND I HAVE BUILT

16:41.634 --> 16:45.732
AND JUST HAND IT OVER
TO BOB WHITMORE...

16:45.734 --> 16:48.198
CHILD,
YOU WILL REGRET IT

16:48.200 --> 16:50.732
FOR THE REST
OF YOUR LIFE.

16:55.134 --> 16:57.132
DON'T DO IT.

16:57.134 --> 17:07.198
♪♪

17:07.200 --> 17:14.365
♪♪

17:17.667 --> 17:21.099
♪♪

17:21.101 --> 17:23.165
CAN YOU GET E-MAILS
IN THERE?

17:23.167 --> 17:24.698
YEAH, IF SOMEONE
GETS YOU A PHONE,

17:24.700 --> 17:26.432
BUT IT'S AGAINST
THE RULES.

17:26.434 --> 17:28.765
YOU CAN GET PUT
IN SOLITARY FOR THAT.

17:28.767 --> 17:31.265
LETTERS?
YEAH, I GUESS.

17:31.267 --> 17:33.265
I'M GOING TO WRITE YOU
ALL THE TIME.

17:33.267 --> 17:34.832
COOL.

17:34.834 --> 17:36.998
UH, AND HOW DO I PUT MONEY
INTO YOUR COMMISSARY ACCOUNT?

17:37.000 --> 17:38.065
I HEARD MOM
TALKING TO AARON ABOUT IT.

17:38.067 --> 17:40.065
LOOK,
DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.

17:40.067 --> 17:42.598
YOU'RE MY BROTHER, AND I'M
GOING TO WORRY ABOUT YOU.

17:42.600 --> 17:43.665
YOU CAN'T STOP ME.

17:43.667 --> 17:45.398
FINE.
JUST DON'T WRITE LETTERS.

17:45.400 --> 17:47.665
DON'T PUT MONEY,
WHATEVER.

17:47.667 --> 17:49.132
JUST FORGET I EXIST.

17:49.134 --> 17:52.065
IT'S BETTER FOR EVERYONE
IF I DIDN'T, ANYWAY.

17:52.067 --> 17:53.598
DON'T SAY THINGS
LIKE THAT.

17:53.600 --> 17:55.265
WAIT,
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

17:55.267 --> 17:56.532
FOR A WALK.
CAN I COME?

17:56.534 --> 17:58.132
NO.

17:58.134 --> 18:02.132
[ CELLPHONE BUZZING ]

18:02.134 --> 18:04.665
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

18:04.667 --> 18:07.465
HEY, CAN I COME OVER?

18:07.467 --> 18:09.365
ALL THOSE IN FAVOR?

18:09.367 --> 18:12.698
Together: AYE.

18:12.700 --> 18:14.765
ALL THOSE OPPOSED.

18:14.767 --> 18:16.432
Together: NAY.

18:27.467 --> 18:29.465
[ SIGHS ]

18:29.467 --> 18:31.499
YOU READY
TO DO THIS?

18:32.600 --> 18:34.531
DO I HAVE TO?

18:34.533 --> 18:36.665
NO, YOU DON'T.

18:36.667 --> 18:43.932
♪♪

18:43.934 --> 18:47.932
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

18:47.934 --> 18:50.532
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

18:50.534 --> 18:53.265
YES?

18:53.267 --> 18:55.932
I WILL, UH...

18:55.934 --> 18:58.932
I'LL --
I'LL LET HER KNOW.

18:58.934 --> 19:02.198
THANK YOU,
MISS DEEFER.

19:02.200 --> 19:04.265
OKAY, GOODBYE.

19:04.267 --> 19:06.532
♪♪

19:06.534 --> 19:07.932
DON'T TELL ME.

19:07.934 --> 19:09.932
AS LONG
AS YOU DON'T SAY THE WORDS,

19:09.934 --> 19:11.732
I'M STILL LIVING
IN A WORLD

19:11.734 --> 19:13.065
THAT LOOKS
SOMETHING LIKE

19:13.067 --> 19:14.865
ONE I UNDERSTAND
OR WANT TO LIVE IN.

19:14.867 --> 19:16.865
♪♪

19:16.867 --> 19:17.998
[ SIGHS ]

19:18.000 --> 19:20.465
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES, BEEPS ]

19:20.467 --> 19:22.265
HELLO?

19:22.267 --> 19:24.265
OH, YES.

19:24.267 --> 19:26.598
OF COURSE.

19:26.600 --> 19:28.165
WHO'S THAT?

19:31.100 --> 19:32.999
UH-HUH.

19:34.434 --> 19:36.532
Y--

19:36.534 --> 19:39.865
WELL,
I WILL BE RIGHT THERE.

19:39.867 --> 19:42.532
NO, THANK<i> YOU.</i>

19:42.534 --> 19:43.565
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

19:43.567 --> 19:45.199
WHO'S THAT?

19:45.201 --> 19:48.132
BOB WHITMORE.

19:48.134 --> 19:49.132
HE WANTS ME

19:49.134 --> 19:52.998
TO COME DOWN
TO THE CHURCH RIGHT NOW TO TALK.

19:53.000 --> 19:56.065
ABOUT WHAT?

19:56.067 --> 19:58.065
THE FUTURE.

20:02.000 --> 20:04.998
HEY, WE HAVE ANY MORE
OF THOSE CRANBERRY PILLS

20:05.000 --> 20:07.465
WE USED TO GIVE ZORA
FOR HER BLADDER INFECTIONS?

20:07.467 --> 20:09.199
WHERE ARE THEY?

20:10.867 --> 20:12.932
YOU DON'T HAVE
A BLADDER INFECTION.

20:12.934 --> 20:14.665
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

20:14.667 --> 20:17.665
CAN YOU JUST SIT DOWN
FOR A SECOND, PLEASE?

20:17.667 --> 20:19.399
WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH YOU?

20:21.667 --> 20:25.065
JACOB, THERE IS REALLY
NO EASY WAY TO SAY THIS.

20:26.400 --> 20:30.132
WELL, FIRST OF ALL,
I, UM...

20:30.134 --> 20:31.932
I LOVE YOU.

20:31.934 --> 20:33.031
OKAY.

20:33.033 --> 20:34.932
NOW YOU'RE SCARING ME.

20:37.467 --> 20:40.399
[ SIGHS ]

20:41.800 --> 20:44.065
I HAVE CHLAMYDIA,

20:44.067 --> 20:45.465
AND YOU
PROBABLY DO, TOO.

20:45.467 --> 20:46.798
YOU HAVE WHAT?!

20:46.800 --> 20:48.532
I HAVE CHLAMYDIA.

20:48.534 --> 20:49.998
CAN YOU JUST SIT DOWN
SO WE CAN TALK --

20:50.000 --> 20:51.598
HOW THE HELL
DID YOU GET CHLAMYDIA?!

20:51.600 --> 20:52.798
JACOB, PLEASE.
HOW?!

20:52.800 --> 20:54.332
JACOB, PLEASE.
JUST SIT DOWN.

20:54.334 --> 20:56.465
JACOB.
JACOB, SIT DOWN.

20:56.467 --> 20:57.532
[ STAMMERS ]

20:57.534 --> 20:59.665
IT'S FERNANDO,
ISN'T IT?

20:59.667 --> 21:01.398
YEAH,
I-I KNEW IT.

21:01.400 --> 21:03.398
WHEN I ASKED YOU

21:03.400 --> 21:07.532
WHY YOU WERE AT HIS OFFICE
THE OTHER DAY, YOU LIED.

21:07.534 --> 21:09.732
SO IS IT
STILL GOING ON?

21:09.734 --> 21:11.532
NO.
IS IT STILL GOING ON?!

21:11.534 --> 21:13.598
NO! NO.

21:13.600 --> 21:14.932
HOW MANY TIMES,
KERISSA?!

21:14.934 --> 21:16.299
JACOB, COME ON!

21:16.301 --> 21:17.431
YOU'VE BEEN RUNNING OFF

21:17.433 --> 21:19.765
TO SOME LITTLE NASTY HOTEL
OR SOMETHING?

21:19.767 --> 21:21.398
WHAT HOTELS
WERE<i> YOU</i> RUNNING TO?!

21:21.400 --> 21:22.865
THAT'S NOT THE QU--
I ASKED<i> YOU!</i>

21:22.867 --> 21:24.932
IF YOU WOULD JUST
LET ME EXPLAIN, JACOB, PLEASE --

21:24.934 --> 21:28.199
I DON'T --
I DON'T EVEN WANT TO KNOW.

21:28.201 --> 21:29.599
JUST GET OUT.

21:29.601 --> 21:30.932
GET OUT WHERE?

21:30.934 --> 21:32.865
I DON'T KNOW.
JUST GET OUT OF THIS HOUSE.

21:32.867 --> 21:34.998
YOU HAVE GOT TO BE
KIDDING ME, JACOB.

21:35.000 --> 21:36.732
COME ON.
DO I LOOK LIKE I'M --

21:36.734 --> 21:38.932
YOU'RE GOING TO KICK ME OUT
FOR CHEATING?

21:38.934 --> 21:40.865
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU KNOW WHAT?

21:40.867 --> 21:42.998
ONE MISTAKE AFTER ALL THE YEARS
I PUT UP WITH YOU -- YOU.

21:43.000 --> 21:44.465
YOU KNOW WHAT,
YOU BEEN WANTING

21:44.467 --> 21:46.065
TO GET OUT OF THIS HOUSE
SO BAD.

21:46.067 --> 21:47.765
GET OUT.
GET OUT!

21:47.767 --> 21:50.432
I NEVER
GAVE YOU A DISEASE.

21:50.434 --> 21:53.365
YOU<i> ARE</i> THE DISEASE,
BOO!

21:53.367 --> 21:55.665
GOING TO KICK ME OUT
OF YOUR MOMMY'S HOUSE.

21:55.667 --> 21:58.065
I AIN'T GOING NOWHERE!

21:58.067 --> 21:59.499
NO-WHERE.

22:03.000 --> 22:06.598
GO AND GET YOURSELF
A LAWYER...

22:06.600 --> 22:11.632
BECAUSE THIS, US,
THIS IS OVER.

22:11.634 --> 22:13.732
OVER!

22:13.734 --> 22:16.065
GOODBYE.

22:16.067 --> 22:18.732
♪♪

22:18.734 --> 22:20.265
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

22:20.267 --> 22:24.632
♪♪

22:24.634 --> 22:27.632
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

22:27.634 --> 22:29.232
♪♪

22:29.234 --> 22:31.065
HI, FERNANDO, IT'S ME.

22:31.067 --> 22:33.932
WAS WONDERING
IF YOU HAD SOME FREE TIME.

22:33.934 --> 22:37.299
I HAVE SOME INTERESTING NEWS
OF MY OWN.

22:41.500 --> 22:44.065
THANKS SO MUCH FOR COMING OVER
ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE.

22:44.067 --> 22:46.199
Y-YOU MUST'VE HEARD

22:46.201 --> 22:48.532
ABOUT OUR PLANS
FOR THE CHURCH, I ASSUME.

22:48.534 --> 22:51.865
YES, I'VE HEARD THERE'S TO BE
SOME KIND OF EXPANSION?

22:51.867 --> 22:54.898
I PLAN TO MAKE THIS SITE
THE HOME

22:54.900 --> 22:57.232
FOR HARMONY & HOPE WORLDWIDE.

22:57.234 --> 22:59.431
I WANT TO RUN
THE WHOLE OPERATION

22:59.433 --> 23:01.098
FROM RIGHT HERE.

23:01.100 --> 23:04.165
MAKE THIS CHURCH,
WITH A FEW IMPROVEMENTS,

23:04.167 --> 23:07.798
THE HOME CHURCH
OF THE WHOLE DENOMINATION.

23:07.800 --> 23:11.798
SO YOU WANT MY PEOPLE,
THE BLACK PEOPLE,

23:11.800 --> 23:13.665
TO GO
TO YOUR WHITE CHURCH?

23:13.667 --> 23:18.998
I WANT ALL PEOPLE,
BLACK, WHITE, WHOEVER,

23:19.000 --> 23:23.432
TO WORSHIP IN RESPECT
AND FREEDOM TOGETHER.

23:24.600 --> 23:26.932
I'M SORRY,
BUT IT WOULDN'T WORK.

23:26.934 --> 23:28.532
NOT WITHOUT YOU.

23:28.534 --> 23:30.198
YOU'RE RIGHT.

23:30.200 --> 23:32.932
I WANT YOU
TO JOIN WITH ME

23:32.934 --> 23:36.798
IN BRINGING H&H
INTO THE FUTURE -- TOGETHER.

23:36.800 --> 23:37.899
YOU AND ME.

23:37.901 --> 23:40.565
FOR THIS VISION
TO SUCCEED,

23:40.567 --> 23:43.032
IT NEEDS A STRONG BLACK LEADER
IN THE PULPIT,

23:43.034 --> 23:44.865
SOMEONE WHO SEES
THE VALUE

23:44.867 --> 23:47.331
OF BREAKING DOWN
THE WALLS OF RACISM

23:47.333 --> 23:50.198
AND GROWING GOD'S KINGDOM.

23:50.200 --> 23:52.732
THIS COULD BE YOU,
MAE.

23:52.734 --> 23:54.532
YOU AND ME.

23:54.534 --> 23:56.865
♪♪

23:56.867 --> 23:59.332
BEFORE I TALK TO YOU ABOUT THAT,
THOUGH, BOB --

23:59.334 --> 24:02.132
[ CHUCKLES ]
IT'S A BIGGIE, RIGHT?

24:02.134 --> 24:03.998
YES, IT IS.

24:04.000 --> 24:06.398
♪♪

24:06.400 --> 24:09.132
BUT I NEED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT GRACE

24:09.134 --> 24:11.132
AND HER SITUATION

24:11.134 --> 24:15.031
AS IT PERTAINS
TO SOMEONE ELSE.

24:15.033 --> 24:18.232
HMM.
AND WHO'S THAT?

24:18.234 --> 24:21.365
YOUR LITTLE FRIEND
PHIL DEMARS.

24:21.367 --> 24:23.699
HMM.

24:23.701 --> 24:26.365
[ SIGHS ]

24:26.367 --> 24:36.265
♪♪

24:36.267 --> 24:40.632
♪♪

24:40.634 --> 24:42.998
WHY DON'T WE TAKE THIS
TO MY ROOM?

24:43.000 --> 24:49.065
♪♪

24:49.067 --> 24:51.932
WHAT'S WRONG?

24:51.934 --> 24:53.932
I'VE NEVER
DONE IT BEFORE.

24:53.934 --> 24:56.332
♪♪

24:56.334 --> 24:58.198
WE DON'T HAVE TO.

24:58.200 --> 25:01.332
NO,
I WANT TO.

25:01.334 --> 25:06.465
♪♪

25:06.467 --> 25:07.932
HEY.

25:07.934 --> 25:11.598
WHENEVER YOU WANT TO STOP,
WE'LL STOP.

25:11.600 --> 25:14.198
IT'S WHATEVER
YOU WANT TO DO.

25:14.200 --> 25:17.198
♪♪

25:17.200 --> 25:18.198
OKAY.

25:18.200 --> 25:20.865
OKAY.

25:20.867 --> 25:30.332
♪♪

25:30.334 --> 25:31.332
♪♪

25:31.334 --> 25:32.699
WHERE DID YOU GET
THIS WILL?

25:32.701 --> 25:34.165
IT'S IN
THE PUBLIC RECORD.

25:34.167 --> 25:35.699
AND WHEN YOU TOLD ME
YOU WERE HAVING TROUBLES

25:35.701 --> 25:37.032
WITH YOUR LANDLADY,
I LOOKED IT UP.

25:37.034 --> 25:38.898
OH, THANK YOU
FOR THINKING OF ME.

25:38.900 --> 25:40.432
OF COURSE.

25:40.434 --> 25:42.199
LOOK AT THIS.

25:42.201 --> 25:44.665
SEE WHERE MRS. DAVIS LEFT
THE ESTATE TO THE GREENLEAFS?

25:44.667 --> 25:46.132
YEAH.
WHAT ABOUT IT?

25:46.134 --> 25:47.465
THIS WILL WAS DRAFTED

25:47.467 --> 25:50.198
LESS THAN A MONTH BEFORE
MRS. DAVIS WAS KILLED.

25:50.200 --> 25:52.332
IN A BOTCHED BURGLARY.
RIGHT?

25:52.334 --> 25:54.065
THAT'S THE STORY.

25:54.067 --> 25:55.932
LOOK AT THE EXECUTOR.

25:58.067 --> 26:01.265
ROBERT McCREADY.

26:01.267 --> 26:03.132
IT SAYS
IN THE FINE PRINT

26:03.134 --> 26:05.532
THIS SUPERSEDES
ALL PREVIOUS WILLS.

26:05.534 --> 26:07.598
WHO GOT THE ESTATE
BEFORE?

26:07.600 --> 26:09.732
NO IDEA.

26:09.734 --> 26:13.499
THE FIRST WILL HAS
RATHER CONVENIENTLY DISAPPEARED.

26:21.734 --> 26:23.899
AND WHAT IS
YOUR INTERESTING NEWS?

26:25.234 --> 26:28.198
YOU...[ CHUCKLES ]

26:28.200 --> 26:31.065
GAVE ME CHLAMYDIA.

26:33.534 --> 26:35.132
[ FOOTSTEPS DEPART ]

26:35.134 --> 26:36.865
[ DOOR OPENS ]

26:36.867 --> 26:46.899
♪♪

26:46.901 --> 26:48.965
♪♪

26:48.967 --> 26:50.965
[ SIGHS ]

26:50.967 --> 26:59.398
♪♪

26:59.400 --> 27:01.732
YOU OKAY?

27:01.734 --> 27:03.598
I'M ALL RIGHT.

27:03.600 --> 27:05.598
♪♪

27:05.600 --> 27:07.598
YOU DON'T SEEM
ALL RIGHT.

27:07.600 --> 27:09.732
♪♪

27:09.734 --> 27:12.998
YEAH, WELL,
THIS TIME TOMORROW,

27:13.000 --> 27:14.998
THAT WON'T BE
A PROBLEM ANYMORE.

27:15.000 --> 27:17.665
♪♪

27:17.667 --> 27:19.932
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

27:19.934 --> 27:23.565
WHY ARE YOU INSISTING
ON TURNING YOURSELF IN?

27:23.567 --> 27:29.932
♪♪

27:29.934 --> 27:32.065
STAY.

27:32.067 --> 27:34.798
I WISH I COULD.

27:34.800 --> 27:37.065
I CAN'T.

27:37.067 --> 27:40.198
♪♪

27:40.200 --> 27:42.198
CAN YOU JUST
TELL ME WHY?

27:42.200 --> 27:44.065
♪♪

27:44.067 --> 27:45.932
YOU DON'T GET
TO KNOW WHY.

27:45.934 --> 27:47.932
♪♪

27:47.934 --> 27:50.598
IT'S LIKE EVERYTHING ELSE
IN THIS WORLD.

27:50.600 --> 27:53.532
♪♪

27:53.534 --> 27:57.798
YOU DON'T GET
TO KNOW WHY.

27:57.800 --> 27:59.665
JUST IS.

27:59.667 --> 28:09.532
♪♪

28:09.534 --> 28:19.532
♪♪

28:19.534 --> 28:29.532
♪♪

28:29.534 --> 28:34.865
♪♪

28:34.867 --> 28:36.865
THE BEST
OF ALL POSSIBLE WORLDS.

28:36.867 --> 28:39.532
WELL, GIVEN THE POSSIBLE WORLDS
WE'VE GOT, YES.

28:39.534 --> 28:42.998
JAMES, WHAT WOULD YOU
PROPOSE WE DO?

28:43.000 --> 28:45.565
TELL EVERYBODY
THAT CONNIE SYKES TOOK A BRIBE?

28:45.567 --> 28:47.631
HAVE YOU WATCHED
THE NEWS LATELY?

28:47.633 --> 28:51.265
IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHAT PEOPLE DO, JAMES.

28:51.267 --> 28:52.598
SO PLEASE LET ME DO

28:52.600 --> 28:54.598
WHAT I CAN STILL DO
TO SAVE OUR CHURCH.

28:54.600 --> 28:57.465
BUT IT WON'T BE
OUR CHURCH.

28:57.467 --> 28:59.931
IT WILL BE
SOMETHING ENTIRELY DIFFERENT.

28:59.933 --> 29:02.932
GOD IS GIVING US A WAY,
JAMES.

29:02.934 --> 29:05.798
GRACE FELL,
BUT HE'S LIFTING ME UP.

29:05.800 --> 29:08.265
AND ALL I NEED
IS THIS CHANCE

29:08.267 --> 29:09.965
TO GET CLOSE ENOUGH
TO BOB WHITMORE,

29:09.967 --> 29:11.465
AND I'M TELLING YOU,
PLEASE, JAMES, PLEASE --

29:11.467 --> 29:13.265
YOUR COCKEYED AMBITION

29:13.267 --> 29:15.732
IS MAKING YOU
JUST PLAIN STUPID.

29:15.734 --> 29:17.898
JAMES.

29:17.900 --> 29:19.132
YOU'D MAKE YOURSELF
AN ORNAMENT

29:19.134 --> 29:21.665
ON THE ARM
OF THIS WHITE CRIMINAL?

29:21.667 --> 29:24.131
I HAVE ALREADY
SAID YES.

29:24.133 --> 29:33.998
♪♪

29:34.000 --> 29:43.998
♪♪

29:44.000 --> 29:45.665
♪♪

29:45.667 --> 29:48.132
I DON'T WANT
TO GO HOME.

29:48.134 --> 29:50.265
THEN DON'T.

29:50.267 --> 29:51.965
STAY OVER.

29:55.000 --> 29:56.198
SORRY.

29:56.200 --> 29:58.998
I AM
OLD-FASHIONED.

29:59.000 --> 30:00.865
OH.

30:00.867 --> 30:02.732
DON'T BE.

30:02.734 --> 30:05.065
I LIKE
OLD-FASHIONED.

30:05.067 --> 30:07.065
OH, YEAH?
MM-HMM.

30:07.067 --> 30:08.398
[ LAUGHS ]

30:08.400 --> 30:10.732
YOU KNOW,
IT GOT ME THINKING.

30:10.734 --> 30:13.198
WHEN I WAS A KID...

30:13.200 --> 30:14.831
I WAS INTO MAGIC.

30:14.833 --> 30:16.699
LIKED IT SO MUCH,
I FLUNKED OUT OF THIRD GRADE.

30:16.701 --> 30:18.031
[ LAUGHS ]

30:18.033 --> 30:20.498
OH, MY DAD
SAW MY REPORT CARD,

30:20.500 --> 30:23.265
HE TOOK ALL MY MAGIC BOOKS
AND BURNED THEM ON THE BARBECUE.

30:23.267 --> 30:25.665
OKAY, THAT'S THE SADDEST
STORY EVER.

30:25.667 --> 30:28.932
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:28.934 --> 30:33.065
IT STILL COULD HAVE
A HAPPY ENDING.

30:33.067 --> 30:35.665
WHAT ARE
YOU TALKING ABOUT?

30:35.667 --> 30:37.465
POOF.

30:37.467 --> 30:39.131
[ LAUGHS ]

30:39.133 --> 30:42.065
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

30:42.067 --> 30:44.298
GET READY
TO SAY THE MAGIC WORD.

30:44.300 --> 30:46.898
AND WHAT IS
THE MAGIC WORD?

30:46.900 --> 30:51.798
WELL,
IN THIS CASE...

30:51.800 --> 30:53.798
"YES."

30:53.800 --> 30:57.198
♪♪

30:57.200 --> 30:59.065
CHARITY BERNICE GREENLEAF...

30:59.067 --> 31:07.598
♪♪

31:07.600 --> 31:09.598
...WILL YOU MARRY ME?

31:09.600 --> 31:11.598
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:11.600 --> 31:21.465
♪♪

31:21.467 --> 31:31.032
♪♪

31:31.034 --> 31:40.865
♪♪

31:40.867 --> 31:50.998
♪♪

31:51.000 --> 31:59.399
♪♪

32:02.700 --> 32:05.098
♪♪

32:05.100 --> 32:05.999
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

32:06.001 --> 32:09.532
HEY, GOT A SECOND
TO TALK LOGISTICS?

32:09.534 --> 32:11.198
YEAH, SURE.
COME ON IN.

32:11.200 --> 32:14.132
I JUST FOUND THE PERFECT SPOT
TO WORSHIP AND TO BUILD.

32:14.134 --> 32:16.732
IT'S LESS THAN A MILE FROM HERE,
A GYMNASTICS CLUB,

32:16.734 --> 32:18.465
120,000 SQUARE FEET,

32:18.467 --> 32:19.865
AND THE OWNER,
WHO LIKES ME,

32:19.867 --> 32:21.332
SAID, "IF YOU'RE
THE MAN IN CHARGE,

32:21.334 --> 32:22.398
YOU CAN HAVE IT FOR -- "

32:22.400 --> 32:24.898
BUT YOU WON'T BE
IN CHARGE.

32:24.900 --> 32:27.199
THERE'S BEEN
A LITTLE CHANGE IN PLANS.

32:27.201 --> 32:29.332
IT'S GOING TO BE
ME AND MAE.

32:29.334 --> 32:31.699
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

32:31.701 --> 32:34.932
MAE TOLD ME
WHAT YOU DID TO GRACE, PHIL.

32:36.100 --> 32:37.298
I HAD A FEELING

32:37.300 --> 32:40.565
THAT YOU HAD MORE OF
A HAND IN IT THAN YOU SAID,

32:40.567 --> 32:43.532
BUT, PHIL,
THAT WAS UNCONSCIONABLE!

32:43.534 --> 32:46.232
OH, BOB,
YOU'VE DONE WORSE YOURSELF.

32:46.234 --> 32:48.398
I'M SORRY,
I DIDN'T QUITE CATCH THAT.

32:48.400 --> 32:50.132
WHAT DID YOU SAY,
PHIL?

32:50.134 --> 32:52.165
WHAT DO I HAVE TO DO
TO CHANGE YOUR MIND?

32:55.334 --> 32:58.332
I HAVE GIVEN YOU
ALL I'VE GOT

32:58.334 --> 33:00.265
FOR OVER 20 YEARS.

33:00.267 --> 33:04.031
FOR 20 YEARS.

33:04.033 --> 33:06.298
ALL I WANT TO DO IS GET OUT
FROM BEHIND MY DESK

33:06.300 --> 33:07.798
AND FINALLY GET BACK

33:07.800 --> 33:10.265
TO MINISTERING
AT MY OWN CHURCH.

33:13.067 --> 33:15.599
SO TELL ME,
BOB...

33:15.601 --> 33:19.398
WHAT DO I HAVE TO DO
TO CHANGE YOUR MIND?

33:19.400 --> 33:21.665
HMM?

33:21.667 --> 33:23.798
NAME IT.

33:23.800 --> 33:33.798
♪♪

33:33.800 --> 33:37.465
♪♪

33:37.467 --> 33:39.865
RIGHT.

33:39.867 --> 33:40.932
RAH. [ LAUGHS ]

33:40.934 --> 33:42.998
GO GET THE BOARD TOGETHER.
I'LL BE RIGHT IN.

33:43.000 --> 33:45.865
NADINE, LET ME CALL YOU
RIGHT BACK.

33:45.867 --> 33:47.798
FIND A PLACE
TO LIVE YET?

33:47.800 --> 33:49.598
I HEAR THERE'S
A BY-THE-HOUR HOTEL AVAILABLE

33:49.600 --> 33:51.865
ON ELVIS PRESLEY BOULEVARD.

33:51.867 --> 33:54.232
I'M STAYING PUT.

33:54.234 --> 33:55.899
OH, REALLY?

33:55.901 --> 33:58.299
AND DON'T YOU EVER
TALK TO ME LIKE THAT AGAIN,

33:58.301 --> 34:01.998
UNLESS YOU WANT BISHOP
TO DIE IN JAIL.

34:02.000 --> 34:03.465
WHAT DRUG ARE YOU ON?

34:03.467 --> 34:05.265
IT'S CALLED TRUTH.

34:05.267 --> 34:06.798
YOU WANT SOME?

34:06.800 --> 34:14.898
♪♪

34:14.900 --> 34:18.798
PHILIP,
WHAT A PLEASANT SURPRISE.

34:18.800 --> 34:21.665
OH, DON'T WASTE YOUR IRONY
ON ME, MAE.

34:21.667 --> 34:23.198
YOU'RE GOING TO NEED IT

34:23.200 --> 34:27.865
WITH SO MANY OTHER
LESS HOPELESS SITUATIONS.

34:27.867 --> 34:29.132
PARDON?

34:29.134 --> 34:30.665
OH, BOB'S GOING TO BE
CALLING YOU SOON

34:30.667 --> 34:32.198
TO TELL YOU
HE'S DEEPLY SORRY,

34:32.200 --> 34:34.998
BUT THE ARRANGEMENT
YOU TWO MADE --

34:35.000 --> 34:37.199
IT'S OFFICIALLY
NULL AND VOID.

34:37.201 --> 34:40.032
I'LL BE RUNNING H&H WITH HIM
GOING FORWARD.

34:42.134 --> 34:43.998
I'LL WAIT
TO HEAR THAT FROM BOB.

34:44.000 --> 34:45.398
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

34:45.400 --> 34:48.665
OH, THAT'S PROBABLY
HIM THERE.

34:48.667 --> 34:50.399
AND ANOTHER THING, MAE,
I KNOW YOU AND JAMES

34:50.401 --> 34:52.998
HAVE A LOT OF PERSONAL
BELONGINGS AT THE CHURCH.

34:53.000 --> 34:55.198
YOU MIGHT WANT
TO GET THOSE OUT.

34:55.200 --> 34:58.398
WHY WOULD SHE
DO THAT?

34:58.400 --> 35:02.265
BECAUSE BARRING A GENERAL OUTCRY
OF THE CONGREGATION,

35:02.267 --> 35:05.198
WE'RE GOING TO
DEMOLISH THE CHURCH IN A WEEK.

35:05.200 --> 35:09.265
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

35:09.267 --> 35:12.865
HEY, [CHUCKLES]
I THOUGHT THAT WAS YOUR CAR.

35:12.867 --> 35:15.332
DID YOU COME OVER
TO ASK PERMISSION?

35:15.334 --> 35:17.865
BECAUSE IT'S A LITTLE LATE
FOR THAT, PHIL.

35:17.867 --> 35:19.398
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

35:19.400 --> 35:21.065
PERMISSION FOR WHAT?

35:24.467 --> 35:27.198
WHAT DO YOU THINK,
MAMA?

35:27.200 --> 35:29.698
TRY TO BE HAPPY
BECAUSE...

35:29.700 --> 35:32.665
IT IS NEVER COMING OFF.

35:32.667 --> 35:34.832
SO DID YOU JUST
STOP BY TO SAY HI?

35:34.834 --> 35:36.465
UH,
NOT ACTUALLY.

35:36.467 --> 35:39.798
THERE'S SOMETHING
WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT...

35:39.800 --> 35:42.665
PRIVATELY.
MM.

35:42.667 --> 35:44.665
WELL,
I LIKE THE SOUND OF THAT.

35:44.667 --> 35:45.932
COME ON.

35:49.467 --> 35:51.432
IF YOU'LL EXCUSE US.

35:56.267 --> 35:59.765
IS HE SERIOUS ABOUT
TEARING DOWN THE CHURCH?

36:02.534 --> 36:04.465
I'M AFRAID THAT HE IS.

36:06.900 --> 36:08.898
OH, I'M SORRY,
GRANDMA.

36:08.900 --> 36:14.532
♪♪

36:14.534 --> 36:17.065
OH.

36:17.067 --> 36:18.932
♪♪

36:18.934 --> 36:20.932
THERE'S NOT GOING TO BE
ANY WEDDING.

36:20.934 --> 36:23.099
♪♪

36:23.101 --> 36:25.165
NOT FOR US, ANYWAY.

36:25.167 --> 36:26.965
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

36:26.967 --> 36:31.998
♪♪

36:32.000 --> 36:33.665
I'M GOING TO MARRY JUDY.

36:33.667 --> 36:39.465
♪♪

36:39.467 --> 36:40.532
BUT LAST NIGHT --

36:40.534 --> 36:42.132
I KNOW.

36:42.134 --> 36:44.732
♪♪

36:44.734 --> 36:47.265
I'M SORRY.

36:47.267 --> 36:51.198
♪♪

36:51.200 --> 36:52.798
GET OUT.

36:52.800 --> 36:54.998
♪♪

36:55.000 --> 36:57.532
PHIL, GET OUT.

36:57.534 --> 36:59.998
GET OUT!

37:00.000 --> 37:09.832
♪♪

37:09.834 --> 37:13.665
♪♪

37:13.667 --> 37:17.698
FATHER, GOD,
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

37:17.700 --> 37:20.432
♪♪

37:20.434 --> 37:23.565
THE CHURCH IS GONE.

37:23.567 --> 37:27.132
OR WILL BE IN SEVEN DAYS' TIME.

37:27.134 --> 37:29.332
MY FAMILY
IS IN COMPLETE DISARRAY.

37:29.334 --> 37:32.332
♪♪

37:32.334 --> 37:35.932
AND MY SON, A.J.,
I DON'T KNOW HOW TO REACH HIM.

37:35.934 --> 37:44.265
♪♪

37:44.267 --> 37:46.398
GOD, I KNOW YOU'RE GOOD.

37:46.400 --> 37:48.998
♪♪

37:49.000 --> 37:51.265
I KNOW THAT YOU SEE MY HEART.

37:51.267 --> 37:53.465
♪♪

37:53.467 --> 37:57.865
I KNOW THAT
YOU HAVE ORDERED MY STEPS.

37:57.867 --> 37:59.798
I KNOW THAT YOU HAVE
CARRIED ME OVER EVERY MOUNTAIN,

37:59.800 --> 38:01.398
THAT YOU'VE LIT MY PATH
IN EVERY VALLEY, LORD,

38:01.400 --> 38:03.065
AND I THANK YOU.
I PRAISE YOU.

38:03.067 --> 38:04.998
FATHER, I THANK YOU.

38:05.000 --> 38:12.398
♪♪

38:12.400 --> 38:15.198
I THANK YOU...

38:15.200 --> 38:17.198
♪♪

38:17.200 --> 38:19.631
...FOR THE BISHOP,

38:19.633 --> 38:26.198
WHO TEACHES ME HOPE
MORE AND MORE ALL THE TIME.

38:26.200 --> 38:28.932
THANK YOU FOR MY MOTHER.

38:28.934 --> 38:33.465
SHE NEVER GIVES UP,
AND I LOVE HER FOR THAT.

38:33.467 --> 38:36.565
♪♪

38:36.567 --> 38:39.965
THANK YOU, LORD
FOR MY DAUGHTER, SOPHIA.

38:39.967 --> 38:41.898
GO AWAY.

38:41.900 --> 38:43.398
[<i> TV CHATTER</i> ]

38:43.400 --> 38:46.998
SHE TEACHES ME COURAGE.

38:47.000 --> 38:50.132
SHE IS
AN EXAMPLE TO ME EVERY DAY.

38:50.134 --> 38:51.532
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

38:51.534 --> 38:56.365
AND JACOB AND KERISSA,
LORD, THANK YOU.

38:56.367 --> 38:59.032
AND FOR THAT BEAUTIFUL NIECE
AND NEPHEW THEY GAVE ME.

38:59.034 --> 39:01.965
♪♪

39:01.967 --> 39:03.832
SO WHAT DO YOU THINK
THIS MEANS?

39:03.834 --> 39:05.565
WELL, I WOULDN'T DARE
TO PRESUME,

39:05.567 --> 39:08.265
BUT IT LOOKS LIKE YOUR PARENTS
HAD MRS. DAVIS KILLED

39:08.267 --> 39:10.265
AND BASICALLY
STOLE THIS HOUSE FROM HER.

39:10.267 --> 39:12.398
DOESN'T IT
LOOK LIKE THAT TO YOU?

39:12.400 --> 39:16.598
♪♪

39:16.600 --> 39:18.732
THANK YOU FOR MY SISTER CHARITY,

39:18.734 --> 39:21.765
FOR ALL SHE IS
AND ALL SHE ISN'T.

39:21.767 --> 39:25.132
♪♪

39:25.134 --> 39:29.132
AND FOR MY SISTER FAITH...

39:29.134 --> 39:31.132
♪♪

39:31.134 --> 39:34.665
...WHO CALLED ME HOME...

39:34.667 --> 39:37.998
SO THAT
I COULD LEARN A LESSON...

39:38.000 --> 39:39.932
I KNOW ISN'T OVER YET.

39:39.934 --> 39:41.899
♪♪

39:41.901 --> 39:44.632
OH, I MISS YOU, SISTER.

39:44.634 --> 39:46.698
I MISS YOU.

39:46.700 --> 39:51.398
♪♪

39:51.400 --> 39:53.665
AND, LORD, ABOUT MY SON...

39:53.667 --> 39:59.665
♪♪

39:59.667 --> 40:01.299
A.J.

40:01.301 --> 40:07.698
♪♪

40:07.700 --> 40:09.698
OH, I'M SORRY.

40:09.700 --> 40:11.765
ARE YOU LOST?

40:11.767 --> 40:13.598
I DON'T THINK SO.

40:13.600 --> 40:15.732
♪♪

40:15.734 --> 40:18.198
HOW'D YOU
GET ON THE PROPERTY?

40:18.200 --> 40:20.465
I JUST STARTED WALKING,
AND I ENDED UP HERE.

40:26.100 --> 40:27.232
FAITH.

40:27.234 --> 40:29.299
SHE WAS YOUR SISTER.

40:33.134 --> 40:35.198
HOW DID YOU KNOW THAT?

40:35.200 --> 40:37.865
THE DATES.

40:37.867 --> 40:40.732
I JUST
TOOK A SHOT.

40:40.734 --> 40:42.732
YEAH,
SHE WAS MY SISTER.

40:49.767 --> 40:52.965
EVERYTHING HAS
AN EXPIRATION DATE.

40:52.967 --> 40:55.065
KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

40:55.067 --> 41:01.932
♪♪

41:01.934 --> 41:03.999
EVERYTHING.

41:04.001 --> 41:08.598
♪♪

41:08.600 --> 41:11.332
YEAH.

41:11.334 --> 41:13.598
THE ROAD
IS BACK THAT WAY.

41:13.600 --> 41:15.132
IT'LL TAKE YOU
TO THE GATE.

41:15.134 --> 41:20.732
♪♪

41:20.734 --> 41:22.798
THANKS FOR
THE DIRECTIONS.

41:22.800 --> 41:24.598
♪♪

41:24.600 --> 41:26.465
I'LL SEE YOU AROUND,
GRACE.

41:26.467 --> 41:36.365
♪♪

